author: Whitney Medworth
title: Jason Terry got so excited throwing an alley-oop he jumped on the scorers table
text:
HAHAHA
Jason Terry is so excited to be on the Bucks. I mean, I can’t blame him when he gets paid to play basketball every night with Jabari Parker and Giannis Antetokounmpo. I’d be pretty excited too.
The JET fuels JAMbari!! #FearTheDeer pic.twitter.com/Om6ykO1ryw 
— Milwaukee Bucks (@Bucks) January 7, 2017 But here’s the thing ... Terry literally got on the scorers table to cheer during a game in January. It’s January.
Never change, JET.
